# llm/

This directory contains LLM-specific guidance files for the Intent project. These are core reference documents that establish coding standards, module ownership, and code placement rules via the Highlander principle.

## Files

- `MODULES.md` -- Module registry enforcing the Highlander Rule; definitive mapping of concerns to Bash scripts and helpers
- `DECISION_TREE.md` -- Code placement decision tree with cross-references to MODULES.md; answers where new code belongs
- `AGENTS.md` -- Development environment, build/test commands, code style, Intent steel thread process, and commit guidelines
